---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<section class="bg-gray-900 text-white p-8 rounded-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold border-b pb-2 mb-6">Farmers Role Overview</h1>

  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
    Once the earth began to decline, Farmers searched for a paradise to help rebuild the wrecked world.
    After being expelled from the Seed Vault, their importance grew. The final generation that worked there weren't fightersâ€”they became supporters of their communities, helping with construction, farming, and protection.
  </p>

  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
    This role fits those who love nature, enjoy helping others, and prefer a supportive role in the action. They do a bit of everything, often giving more than receiving.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Background Bonuses</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-1">
    <li><strong>Medicine:</strong> Heals plants and potentially other players.</li>
    <li><strong>Foraging:</strong> Knows which plants are safe, edible, or medicinal.</li>
    <li><strong>Reaction:</strong> Capable of fighting, but not a trained warrior.</li>
    <li><strong>Sneakiness:</strong> Acute hearing developed from years working with plants.</li>
    <li><strong>Deduction:</strong> Highly intelligent and good at passing down stories.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Unique Skill</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-300">
    <strong>Revive:</strong> The ability to bring plants back to life.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Equipment</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-1">
    <li><strong>Canteen:</strong> Used for watering seeds or people.</li>
    <li><strong>Satchel:</strong> Carries the canteen, gel, and seeds.</li>
    <li><strong>White Gel:</strong> A mysterious ointment that can become medicine.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">NPC Connection</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-300">
    Farmers are familiar with <strong>Ernest Elderberry</strong>, a village elder who provides guidance and information.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2">Cybernetics, Tracking & Fear Skills</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-gray-300">
    <!-- Cybernetics -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Cybernetics</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
        <li>Rank 1: +1 cybernetics check</li>
        <li>Rank 2: Hack basic locks without checks</li>
        <li>Rank 3: +3 to recover or decrypt files</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Tracking -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Tracking</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
        <li>Rank 1: Know where someone went</li>
        <li>Rank 2: Track up to a mile</li>
        <li>Rank 3: Predict next destination</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Fear -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Fear</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
        <li>Rank 1: +2 to info-gathering fear checks</li>
        <li>Rank 2: 1 psychic harm (ignores armor)</li>
        <li>Rank 3: Add fear mod to attacks</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
